 feet, 1\\u00be inches, Crouser capped his most challenging season with perhaps his most rewarding victory under the lights and pressure from his body, but never pressure from competitors.\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 935, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a winning throw\", \"from\": 732, \"to\": 747}, {\"ngram\": \"75 feet\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 758}, {\"ngram\": \"1\\u00be inches\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 769}, {\"ngram\": \"Crouser\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 778}, {\"ngram\": \"his most challenging season\", \"from\": 786, \"to\": 813}, {\"ngram\": \"perhaps his most rewarding victory\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 853}, {\"ngram\": \"the lights\", \"from\": 860, \"to\": 870}, {\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 883}, {\"ngram\": \"his body\", \"from\": 889, \"to\": 897}, {\"ngram\": \"never pressure\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 917}, {\"ngram\": \"competitors\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 934}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After enduring through an ulnar nerve injury in his throwing elbow in March, and a pectoral muscle tear in April, he arrived in Paris coming off of his first loss in 10 months yet still believing that \\\"at the top end I can still be as good as I ever was, if not better,\\\" he said this week.\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 1225, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1064, \"end\": 1069, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8153942468473965e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an ulnar nerve injury\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 980}, {\"ngram\": \"his throwing elbow\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 1002}, {\"ngram\": \"March\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1011}, {\"ngram\": \"a pectoral muscle tear\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1039}, {\"ngram\": \"April\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1048}, {\"ngram\": \"his first loss\", \"from\": 1084, \"to\": 1098}, {\"ngram\": \"10 months\", \"from\": 1102, \"to\": 1111}, {\"ngram\": \"the top end\", \"from\": 1141, \"to\": 1152}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He backed it up during the final.\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1260, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the final\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1259}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His first-attempt throw of 74 feet, 3\\u00bd inches would have been far enough to win on its own, but then he improved on his next two throws.\", \"from\": 1261, \"to\": 1397, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His first-attempt throw\", \"from\": 1261, \"to\": 1284}, {\"ngram\": \"74 feet\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1295}, {\"ngram\": \"3\\u00bd inches\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1306}, {\"ngram\": \"his next two throws\", \"from\": 1377, \"to\": 1396}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The self-doubt, the injuries that went into this makes me appreciate it all the more,\\\" Crouser said.\", \"from\": 1399, \"to\": 1500, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the injuries\", \"from\": 1416, \"to\": 1428}, {\"ngram\": \"Crouser\", \"from\": 1487, \"to\": 1494}]}, {\"sentence\": \"American Joe Kovacs earned the silver medal and Brazil's Rajindra Campbell took the bronze, with each throwing 72-8.\", \"from\": 1502, \"to\": 1618, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1502, \"end\": 1510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9323494089087391, \"rank\": 0.07255239173883132, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1511, \"end\": 1514, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\", \"score\": 0.9999999983888301, \"rank\": 1.6073099662552375e-09, \"text\": \"Joe\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\"}, {\"begin\": 1550, \"end\": 1556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score